data.description: 6% assumable loan, Beautiful Home, on corner lot. Open concept Living room, dining room and kitchen. Kitchen has a door to deck and newly fenced back yard. Also, 3 bedrooms and updated full bath on main level. Lower level offers laundry room, family room and 1/2 bath. Updates include HVAC 2017, garage doors, siding, exterior lights, garbage disposal, water heater and front railing. 2023 Beautiful fence was added. In last year Interior painting has been done and is almost completed on main level. Close to major highways, Austin Landing, Dayton Mall, Restaurants, shopping. Miamisburg Schools! Move in ready, immediate occupancy. Motivated seller!
